<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 14:07:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>假婴儿，真正的恐怖：加沙战争的 Deepfake 增加了人们对人工智能误导能力的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/deepfakes-from-the-gaza-war-increase-fears-about-ais-power-to-mislead/0000018c-3a07-dc03-a9ec-3e7fadf10000</link><description>社交媒体帐户正在利用人工智能传播有关以色列-加沙战争的错误信息，专家担心这对冲突的未来意味着什么</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 13:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/deepfakes-from-the-gaza-war-increase-fears-about-ais-power-to-mislead/0000018c-3a07-dc03-a9ec-3e7fadf10000</guid></item><item><title>尽管以色列情报部门警告哈马斯可能发动袭击，但军队并未撤离诺瓦节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/despite-intel-warnings-about-a-hamas-attack-the-army-didnt-evacuate-the-nova-festival/0000018c-3993-dc03-a9ec-3dfb2cda0000</link><description>10 月 7 日前一天晚上，高级国防官员就哈马斯可能发动的袭击举行了紧急磋商。但以色列国防军中没有人通知新星节组织者或参加聚会的人，数百人被砍倒——在九个小时的时间里，没有人来拯救他们</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 13:41:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/despite-intel-warnings-about-a-hamas-attack-the-army-didnt-evacuate-the-nova-festival/0000018c-3993-dc03-a9ec-3dfb2cda0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，哈马斯火箭在靠近核火箭储存设施的以色列基地引发火灾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/hamas-rockets-on-oct-7-spark-fire-near-nuclear-capable-rocket-storage-facility/0000018c-39ea-dc03-a9ec-3dfb70980000</link><description>以色列对其核能力维持战略模糊政策。以色列中部的斯多特米查基地于 10 月 7 日遭受火箭弹袭击，严重受损，该基地部署有以色列可携带核弹头的杰里科导弹</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 13:19:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/hamas-rockets-on-oct-7-spark-fire-near-nuclear-capable-rocket-storage-facility/0000018c-39ea-dc03-a9ec-3dfb70980000</guid></item><item><title>美国顶尖大学校长将因对校园反犹太主义的反应而受到国会盘问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/heads-of-top-u-s-universities-to-be-grilled-by-congress-over-response-to-antisemitism/0000018c-3995-dc03-a9ec-3dff193b0000</link><description>哈佛大学、麻省理工学院和宾夕法尼亚大学校长将于周二出席听证会，要求校园领导负起责任并对抗反犹太主义</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 11:39:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/heads-of-top-u-s-universities-to-be-grilled-by-congress-over-response-to-antisemitism/0000018c-3995-dc03-a9ec-3dff193b0000</guid></item><item><title>周一，五名以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-monday-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-3966-dc03-a9ec-3d7fe0ab0000</link><description>周二早些时候，以色列国防军宣布三名士兵被杀，但后来又公布了周一被杀的另外两名士兵的名字</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 11:02:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-monday-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-3966-dc03-a9ec-3d7fe0ab0000</guid></item><item><title>照片中的 2023 年：极端气候</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/year-end/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/2023-in-photos-extreme-climate/0000018c-39a3-d5f2-a5cc-7fb7ca920000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 11:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/year-end/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/2023-in-photos-extreme-climate/0000018c-39a3-d5f2-a5cc-7fb7ca920000</guid></item><item><title>母女乌干达之旅成为犹太人的反思</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/a-mother-daughter-trip-to-uganda-becomes-a-reflection-on-being-a-jew/0000018c-3926-d11b-a3bf-ffaf237e0000</link><description>纪录片《谁像你一样？》中非洲阿巴尤达亚社区之旅产生了意想不到的结果– 在耶路撒冷即将举行的犹太电影周上放映</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 10:59:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/a-mother-daughter-trip-to-uganda-becomes-a-reflection-on-being-a-jew/0000018c-3926-d11b-a3bf-ffaf237e0000</guid></item><item><title>德国和奥地利主要评论员抨击联合国未能解决哈马斯针对妇女的罪行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/german-austrian-commentators-slam-toothless-un-over-failure-to-address-hamas-crimes/0000018c-395d-de12-a3af-3bddf4d80000</link><description>巴黎恐怖袭击引发人们对伊斯兰原教旨主义抬头的担忧，德国媒体试图追究联合国未能解决针对以色列妇女的性暴力问题的责任</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 10:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/german-austrian-commentators-slam-toothless-un-over-failure-to-address-hamas-crimes/0000018c-395d-de12-a3af-3bddf4d80000</guid></item><item><title>报告称，哈马斯可能在 10 月 7 日袭击之前使用间谍侦察以色列国防军基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/hamas-may-have-used-spy-to-scout-idf-base-before-oct-7-attack-report-says/0000018c-3980-de12-a3af-3bcdbc260000</link><description>根据战斗后恢复的地图，一名以色列官员告诉《卫报》，文件中发现的详细程度暗示了该设施的“内部知识”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 10:42:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/hamas-may-have-used-spy-to-scout-idf-base-before-oct-7-attack-report-says/0000018c-3980-de12-a3af-3bcdbc260000</guid></item><item><title>报告称，以色列正在讨论使用海水淹没加沙隧道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/israel-debating-using-seawater-to-flood-gaza-tunnels-report-says/0000018c-3909-dc03-a9ec-3d7b120a0000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，以色列为此目的组装了一个大型水泵系统，并于上个月向美国提交了该计划。埃及过去曾成功地利用海水淹没加沙隧道，但由于所有人的目光都集中在以色列，一些人对后果和国际反应表示担忧</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:42:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/israel-debating-using-seawater-to-flood-gaza-tunnels-report-says/0000018c-3909-dc03-a9ec-3d7b120a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡腐败审判的法官接受因战争而减少听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/judges-in-netanyahu-corruption-trial-accept-reduction-of-hearings-due-to-war/0000018c-393d-d11b-a3bf-ffbd56ee0000</link><description>审判的最后一次听证会于 9 月举行，此后法庭因节日休庭。 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击后，整个法院系统暂停了除紧急案件外的所有诉讼程序，包括对总理的审判</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:26:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/judges-in-netanyahu-corruption-trial-accept-reduction-of-hearings-due-to-war/0000018c-393d-d11b-a3bf-ffbd56ee0000</guid></item><item><title>强奸作为战争武器：犹太妇女呼吁联合国对抗哈马斯的性暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-and-jewish-women-implore-a-reticent-un-to-confront-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-369b-dc03-a9ec-3efbfcb90000</link><description>经过备受批评的沉默之后，联合国召开了首次特别会议，讨论 10 月 7 日大屠杀期间“有预谋和有计划”使用性暴力的问题。发言者包括希拉里·克林顿、谢丽尔·桑德伯格和以色列官员，他们介绍了迄今为止收集到的证据</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-and-jewish-women-implore-a-reticent-un-to-confront-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-369b-dc03-a9ec-3efbfcb90000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯被释放的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/the-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity/0000018c-0fb3-d65f-a7dd-fff736090000</link><description>100 多名以色列人和外国人质于 10 月 7 日在加沙被绑架后已获释或获救。这份确认的名单将不断更新</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 08:51:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/the-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity/0000018c-0fb3-d65f-a7dd-fff736090000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队挺进加沙南部，逼近主要目标：哈马斯辛瓦尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-thrusts-into-southern-gaza-and-closes-in-on-its-main-target-hamas-sinwar/0000018c-36b5-dc03-a9ec-3eff4d9a0000</link><description>两个月的战斗已经大大削弱了哈马斯的实力，但底线是它仍在继续战斗，并且没有表现出任何愿意放下武器的迹象</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-thrusts-into-southern-gaza-and-closes-in-on-its-main-target-hamas-sinwar/0000018c-36b5-dc03-a9ec-3eff4d9a0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙火箭弹袭击以色列南部和中部，造成三人轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article-live/idf-gearing-up-for-ground-offensive-in-southern-gaza-hamas-says-death-toll-tops-15-800/0000018c-37f5-d11b-a3bf-f7fd02e20000</link><description>报告：以色列考虑淹没哈马斯地下隧道的计划 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部表示，自停火结束以来，已有 316 名巴勒斯坦人被杀 ■ 以色列国防军公布了周日在加沙战斗中丧生的三名士兵的姓名 ■ 21 岁的以色列思想在加沙被绑架被宣告死亡 ■ 以色列军队表示，自加沙地面行动开始以来，已找到 800 个哈马斯隧道竖井 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 137 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙至少有 15,899 人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 03:20:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article-live/idf-gearing-up-for-ground-offensive-in-southern-gaza-hamas-says-death-toll-tops-15-800/0000018c-37f5-d11b-a3bf-f7fd02e20000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-36f1-dc03-a9ec-3efb02a20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 22:30:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-36f1-dc03-a9ec-3efb02a20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯人被要求给出一些明确的答案。这里有一些</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israeli-arabs-are-being-asked-to-give-some-clear-answers-here-are-a-few/0000018c-3662-de12-a3af-3fefda8b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 22:06:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israeli-arabs-are-bei